'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da cewa sun zama kamar mugaye
Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi mamakin batun da aka gabatar na sauya sunan su zuwa 'Members of the Welsh Parliament' (MMA).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga shirin da ake yi na sauya sunan Majalisar Dokokin Wales.
'Yan siyasa daga ko'ina cikin siyasa sun damu cewa wannan zai zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisa ya bayyana cewa kungiyarsa ta damu matuka saboda sabon sunan yana da alaƙa da "Tup and Wudleeb".
