A cewar wani dan jam'iyyar Plaid, duk kungiyar ba ta yi farin ciki ba kuma ta ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin da za a bi.
Wani wakilin jam'iyyar Welsh Conservative ya ce kungiyarsa ba ta da wata manufa game da sauya sunan, amma ya lura cewa sabon sunan na MWP yana da wasu maganganu masu kama da "mumpet".
A wannan mahallin, ana furta harafin W a harshen Welsh kamar yadda ake furta U a harshen Yorkshire.
A wani bayani da aka fitar daga hukumar majalisar, wacce a yanzu haka ke tsara dokar da za ta sauya sunan, an ce: "A bayyane yake cewa za a yanke hukunci na karshe kan duk wasu sunaye da za a yi amfani da su wajen kiran mambobin majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta baiwa Majalisar Wakilai ta Wales ikon canza sunan ta.
