Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara jerin tarurrukan neman zaben a wannan dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump ya shirya, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wasu wurare da aka sani, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake jinkirta kada kuri'ar tabbatarwa a zabensa na cike gurbin da ya rage a kotun koli, Trump na da niyyar tallafawa zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon da suke da shi a majalisar dokoki a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron gangamin Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon ta yanar gizo?
Ziyarar Trump zuwa Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya ta a karfe 7 na yammacin yamma a wannan Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon ziyarar Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a kasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump zai iya duba shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon na wanda aka zaɓa a matsayin babban alkali, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya haifar da tashin hankali saboda zargin da ake yi masa na lalata da ita, wanda ya hana majalisar dattijai ta amince da shi har zuwa mako guda, yayin da FBI ke ci gaba da bincike.
Amma dai, babban burin wannan jerin zanga-zanga shi ne, a taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu karfin gwiwa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, a cikin sanarwar da aka fitar a lokacin yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa, an bayyana cewa, wannan taro na masu ba da agaji da kuma masu goyon baya, zai taimaka wa 'yan jam'iyyar Republican wajen kare da kuma kara yawan kujerun da suke da su a majalisar wakilai da kuma majalisar dattawa.
"Sarrafa mulki a Majalisa na da muhimmanci ga shirinsa, har shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama, kuma za mu shiga wani lokaci na kamfen mai cike da alkawura", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya musanta yin magana a kan lamarin.
Taron da aka shirya a yau da dare a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, na iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jan hankalin 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai kai ziyara ta biyu a wannan watan a jihar West Virginia, inda ya lashe kashi 40 cikin 100 na 'yan takara a 2016.
Trump ya yi kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattawa na West Virginia, dan Republican Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya kasa a kididdigar zabe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya ba shi ci gaba a binciken zamantakewa", in ji Simon Heather, masanin ilimin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
