Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai tara dubun dubatan mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, wanda ba kawai za su ji dadin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma za su koyi game da ainihin burin taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci nan da 2030.
Bikin 'Global Citizen' wanda aka kaddamar a shekara ta 2012 ya kasance ci gaba ne na shirin 'Global Poverty', wata kungiyar kare hakkin bil'adama ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da shi.
