"Shugaban ya gudanar da karin zaman tambayoyi da amsoshi fiye da duk wani shugaba da ya taba yi", in ji ta, tana mai cewa, ba tare da ta fadi wata hujja ba: "Mun bincika wadannan alkaluman".
Za a ci gaba da yin taron manema labarai, Sanders ya ci gaba, amma idan 'yan jarida suka sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, wannan ya fi kyau fiye da yin magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan a kai a kai, kuma kun ga muna yin hakan a kai a kai a cikin 'yan makonnin nan, kuma hakan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai, bayan da kuka samu damar yin magana da shugaban Amurka.
Trump ya sha amsa tambayoyi a duk lokacin da ya fita daga fadar White House ko kuma ya halarci taron jama'a ko kuma taron manema labarai tare da manyan baki.
