Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta addabi birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda hukumomi suka sanar, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, kungiyoyin agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala, yankin arewacin Palau, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da tsibirin Sulawesi da kuma Dongal:
Palou babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, wanda ke ƙarshen bakin rairayin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, yana da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Wannan birni ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwa ne lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wata hukuma ce da ke da nisan sama da kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, yawan mutanen yankin, wanda ke da karamin yanki fiye da lardin, ya kai kimanin mutane 299,200.
Fishing da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ma'adinai na nickel ma yana da mahimmanci ga lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Moroglia, a gefen gabar Sulawesi.
An samu ambaliyar tsunami a yankin Palu da Donggala a shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Dawowar Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gine-gine a Dongle.
Tsunami ya sake mamaye yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin "zirin wuta na Pacific" kuma a kai a kai girgizar ƙasa tana aukuwa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a ranar 26 ga Disamba a gabar tekun gabar tekun Aceh a lardin Sumatra ta yammacin Indonesia ta haifar da tsunami da ta mamaye kasashe 14 kuma ta kashe mutane 226,000 a duk fadin tekun na Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A jerin girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar tekun yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Guguwar ruwa mai girman 6.8 ta afka tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ta yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane 700 a gabar tekun.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai rauni ya afkawa yankin Pidi Jaya a Aceh, inda ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici, yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
A wannan karon ba a samu tsunami ba, amma an samu fiye da mutum 100 da suka mutu sanadiyyar rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Wannan girgizar ta rushe gine-gine da yawa kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale.
