Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa kan wani da ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov wanda ake zargi da kai harin da ya kashe mutane 8 a New York, hukuncin da ba a taba yin amfani da shi ba a cikin wannan jihar a kan aikata laifi na tarayya da aka aikata a shekara ta 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da wata babbar mota da aka yi hayar ta Home Depot, ya yi wannan harin a watan Oktoba a kan titin keke da ke kusa da babbar hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da keke da masu tafiya a kan hanya.
Don samun hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi kisan kai da gangan ga mutane takwas kuma ya yi kisan kai da gangan ga mutane da dama, kamar yadda sanarwar da aka bayar game da hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a Kudancin New York.
A cewar takardar shari'ar, duk tuhumar da aka yi wa mutum za ta kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da tuhuma 22 da suka hada da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai da suka shafi zamba da ake amfani da su a wajen masu aikata manyan laifuka da kuma tuhume-tuhume na lalata da motoci.
Wannan hari ya bukaci "tanadi da dabara", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna mai bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan ta'asa, da mugunta da kuma lalata.
"Saifullo Habibulovich Saipov ya jawo rauni, lalacewa da asara ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anne-Laure Decad, Darren Drake, Ariel Earle, Ernan Felucci da Alejandro Damian Panuko", in ji sanarwar.
Mutane biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da Kudancin New York ke neman hukuncin kisa.
An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu dillalai biyu, amma daga baya aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumban 2009.
A cikin shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke wa wani mutum hukuncin kisa a New York a kan wani da'awar da ake yi wa gwamnatin tarayya.  Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata ne da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan aikata laifin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Baki, shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna jin tausayin kansa ba a cikin kwanaki ko watanni bayan harin, kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin takardun shari'a.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji daɗi da ya yi hakan, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saiipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya yi tunanin kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a kan wayar salula, in ji tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a saka masa tutar kungiyar ISIL a cikin dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai aikata laifin ba a kan tuhumar da ake masa da laifin aikata laifuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaicin matakin da lauyoyin suka dauka.
"A ganinmu, yanke hukuncin kisa maimakon yanke hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da samun damar yin zaman lafiya ba, zai kara tsawaita tasirin wadannan abubuwa ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patten.
Kungiyar kare Saipov a baya ta nemi a hana masu shigar da kara da hukuncin kisa.
